              <div class="submitted"><img height="14" width="14" alt="" src="/sites/default/files/pictures/avn/date.png" /> 18.09.2011 <b>//</b> <img height="14" width="14" src="/sites/default/files/pictures/avn/author.png" alt="" /> Jiddu</div>
      	  
